Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.06,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How far we've come
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.60,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How much we've changed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:56.34,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A thousand nights and a million tears
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:10:03.94,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Now I can say that I've conquered my fear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:10.07,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If I could go back, what would I tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:13.97,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Wish you'd listen to the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:22.31,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Till then I'll be patiently waiting right here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.66,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Promises are kept deep in the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:05.85,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Bells are ringing so loud
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.66,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Our spirits will never die
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:18.99,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As long as there is something worth fighting for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.30,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We won't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:25.72,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if the stars falling down
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:30.19,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if the stars crash and burn the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:37.10,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We'll believe our voice will reach the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:41.38,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We won't give up till the end
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:45.98,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We won't give up till we smile again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.01,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Cuz we're alive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:54.65,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Cuz we made a promise to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.49,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.90,chaqu,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.06,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即便遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.60,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即便面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:56.34,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}經過數千個黑夜 落下數萬顆淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:10:03.94,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}此時我自信地說 我戰勝了恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:10.07,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能回到過去 我該對你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:13.97,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}為了讓你聽到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:22.31,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我將永遠在這裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.66,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們恪守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:05.85,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}警報高聲響起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.66,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們的靈魂永生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:18.99,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要還有意義 我們便戰鬥不息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.30,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}永不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:25.72,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即便繁星隕落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:30.19,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}墜落在地 熊熊燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:37.10,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們的聲音也定能響徹宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:41.38,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不到最後一刻 決不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:45.98,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不到重拾笑顏 決不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.01,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因為我們還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:54.65,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因為我們對世界許下了承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.49,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}許下了承諾
